13#include <memory>

15#include "modules/audio_processing/transient/transient_suppressor_impl.h"

17namespace webrtc {
18
19std::unique_ptr<TransientSuppressor> CreateTransientSuppressor(
20 const ApmSubmoduleCreationOverrides& overrides) {
21#ifdef WEBRTC_EXCLUDE_TRANSIENT_SUPPRESSOR
22 return nullptr;
23#else
24 if (overrides.transient_suppression) {
25 return nullptr;
26 }
27 return std::make_unique<TransientSuppressorImpl>();
28#endif
29}
